summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Third Avenue Northwest from West Sixtieth Street to West Sixty seventh Street et al in the City of Seattle, by laying watermains under Ordinance No. 17940, creating Local Improvement District No. 1694 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
